  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/aa0e15e62a8d1aab6a48e711a1e115dc.poster.avif?t=1729193764\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/aa0e15e62a8d1aab6a48e711a1e115dc.webm?t=1729193764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/aa0e15e62a8d1aab6a48e711a1e115dc.mp4?t=1729193764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i>It is the year 30ZZ and ultracorporations have been ruling the world for hundreds of years already.</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/4a5c610fa242d83a9ca6971eef21bdc7.poster.avif?t=1729193764\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/4a5c610fa242d83a9ca6971eef21bdc7.webm?t=1729193764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/4a5c610fa242d83a9ca6971eef21bdc7.mp4?t=1729193764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>ULTIMATE ARMORED TURBODRIFTER ~ SaGa Chapter 2 ~【TANK AUTHORITY WOLFRAM】</strong> is a third person drifting game with a twist. You are racing not against other racers but against the inevitable hand of the corporate market trying to destroy you. Also, you are piloting a highly advanced D.R.I.F.T. tank, specially meant for speed, power and durability. This is your 9-5 day job so make sure to leave a good impression as you try to survive an onslaught of police assaults.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/6f376431f24378309d99548f56da441f.poster.avif?t=1729193764\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/6f376431f24378309d99548f56da441f.webm?t=1729193764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/6f376431f24378309d99548f56da441f.mp4?t=1729193764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/5eb94db7bf037d7fe1dfd6ed67adab05.webp?t=1729193764\" width=500 height=60 /></span><br><br><i>It is the year 30ZZ and ultracorporations have been ruling the world for hundreds of years already.</i><br><br>You are a home-office (the corporation owns your apartment) remote pseudo temp-worker for the Hyperloop conglomerate, and your job is to drive tankdrones onto public corpo-highways to sabotage the public opinion of cars and directly damage the bottom line of Car-Nation, the city-continent whose main export is cars and everything car related.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/bf3eef39116deb683957b1dd3b3a4654.poster.avif?t=1729193764\" width=500 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/bf3eef39116deb683957b1dd3b3a4654.webm?t=1729193764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850410/extras/0ee64d3ad28f34b8474a9d74bd6d2e06.webp?t=1729193764\" width=500 height=60 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Drift through the public corpo-highways!<br></li><li>Destroy and damage anything car-adjacent! This is how your wage is calculated.<br></li><li>Upgrade your tank to be even more destructively efficient and look cooler! Your coolness factor directly influences your final payout.<br></li><li>Be careful of the police and enemy corporate agents!<br></li><li>Invest in the virtual stock cybermarket!<br></li><li>Sick A.C.I.D. trance soundtrack!</li></ul>",
